ied":1679482628},"last_reply_by":"i386","last_touched":1686579210,"title":"毕业旅行和女朋友去新疆，跟小团游有什么注意事项？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/947942","created":1686541701,"deleted":0,"content":"各位 V 友，计划下周和女朋友一起去新疆毕业旅行，跟个小团。但是在网上看着各个团五花八门，也没有去过和了解过新疆，看不懂区别。\r\n\r\n请问各位，有没有跟过的小团推荐？或者教教我该从哪些方面考虑与筛选。谢过各位！\r\n\r\n时间是下周，时长除去来回，计划 5-7 天，从北京过去。预算不包括路费的话，单人 4000 以内","content_rendered":"<p>各位 V 友，计划下周和女朋友一起去新疆毕业旅行，跟个小团。但是在网上看着各个团五花八门，也没有去过和了解过新疆，看不懂区别。</p>\n<p>请问各位，有没有跟过的小团推荐？或者教教我该从哪些方面考虑与筛选。谢过各位！</p>\n<p>时间是下周，时长除去来回，计划 5-7 天，从北京过去。预算不包括路费的话，单人 4000 以内</p>\n","last_modified":1686541701,"replies":85,"id":947942},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":56537,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8420,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":72419,"username":"archxm","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/archxm","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"北京","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6fb7/882c/72419_mini.png?m=1466562054","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6fb7/882c/72419_normal.png?m=1466562054","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6fb7/882c/72419_large.png?m=1466562054","created":1409373064,"last_modified":1466562054},"last_reply_by":"id80108900","last_touched":1686595707,"title":"35+被裁本质上是轮流上岗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/947859","created":1686531537,"deleted":0,"content":"- 首先，别担心，你不会找不到工作。\r\n- 应届生找工作困难，如果他们找不到工作，会出现不稳定。\r\n- 大学生找不到工作，家里打击很大，大家会对这个社会机制产生怀疑。\r\n- 所以，应届生一定要控制好就业率。\r\n- 35+的人，特别 40 的，工作效率是最高的。\r\n- 假如裁掉一个 35+的，那么就要继续招聘 4 个应届生。\r\n- 所以你猜怎么着？","content_rendered":"<ul>\n<li>首先，别担心，你不会找不到工作。</li>\n<li>应届生找工作困难，如果他们找不到工作，会出现不稳定。</li>\n<li>大学生找不到工作，家里打击很大，大家会对这个社会机制产生怀疑。</li>\n<li>所以，应届生一定要控制好就业率。</li>\n<li>35+的人，特别 40 的，工作效率是最高的。</li>\n<li>假如裁掉一个 35+的，那么就要继续招聘 4 个应届生。</li>\n<li>所以你猜怎么着？</li>\n</ul>\n","last_modified":1686531537,"replies":79,"id":947859},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785","name":"life","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785","title":"生活","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","topics":4461,"footer":"","header":"生活中的技术讨论","title_alternative":"Life","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","stars":1142,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":557,"parent_node_name":""},"member":{"id":211883,"username":"AManOnShelf","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/AManOnShelf","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c482/feb6/211883_mini.png?m=1686537714","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c482/feb6/211883_normal.png?m=1686537714","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c482/feb6/211883_large.png?m=1686537714","created":1485095715,"last_modified":1686537714},"last_reply_by":"exploreexe","last_touched":1686584586,"title":"上海买老房子还值吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/947907","created":1686537732,"deleted":0,"content":"最近老爸正式退休，爸妈准备搬到上海来定居，于是买房的事情又提上了日程。  \r\n经过一两周的高密度看房之后，他们在上周六看到一套让他们很上头的房子。  \r\n\r\n房子位置在虹口区地铁站附近，三房 160 多平报价 1150 万，经各方打听房主心理底价是 1070 万。  \r\n这个小区去年 10 月成交过一套同样户型的，价格是 1130 万。  \r\n爸妈心动的点是三房有电梯、离地铁近、装修的好有地暖。  \r\n缺点是 96 年的小区楼龄老、朝向东没有南阳台、停车难、对口小学初中很差。  \r\n\r\n我妈现在特别上头，想要 1070 万马上把合同签下来，生怕错过了这套。。。  \r\n我的想法是再等等，下半年应该能再跌一些。这套最好能 1000 万左右打包拿下。  \r\n\r\n大家觉得呢？今后上海的房价会怎么走？  \r\n \r\n不过今天再想想，四十年之后等我老了，房子肯定不值钱了。  \r\n现在不管 1000 万还是 1100 万，都是接盘。。。干脆多花 100 万买个父母开心算了。","content_rendered":"<p>最近老爸正式退休，爸妈准备搬到上海来定居，于是买房的事情又提上了日程。<br/>\n经过一两周的高密度看房之后，他们在上周六看到一套让他们很上头的房子。  </p>\n<p>房子位置在虹口区地铁站附近，三房 160 多平报价 1150 万，经各方打听房主心理底价是 1070 万。<br/>\n这个小区去年 10 月成交过一套同样户型的，价格是 1130 万。<br/>\n爸妈心动的点是三房有电梯、离地铁近、装修的好有地暖。<br/>\n缺点是 96 年的小区楼龄老、朝向东没有南阳台、停车难、对口小学初中很差。  </p>\n<p>我妈现在特别上头，想要 1070 万马上把合同签下来，生怕错过了这套。。。<br/>\n我的想法是再等等，下半年应该能再跌一些。这套最好能 1000 万左右打包拿下。  </p>\n<p>大家觉得呢？今后上海的房价会怎么走？  </p>\n<p>不过今天再想想，四十年之后等我老了，房子肯定不值钱了。<br/>\n现在不管 1000 万还是 1100 万，都是接盘。。。干脆多花 100 万买个父母开心算了。</p>\n","last_modified":1686537866,"replies":71,"id":947907},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785","name":"life","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785","title":"生活","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","topics":4461,"footer":"","header":"生活中的技术讨论","title_alternative":"Life","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","stars":1142,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":557,"parent_node_name":""},"member":{"id":55506,"username":"Wockee","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Wockee","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9ca22bee0de7865c1b767464dee64cff?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9ca22bee0de7865c1b767464dee64cff?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9ca22bee0de7865c1b767464dee64cff?s=73&d=retro","created":1391860597,"last_modified":1391860597},"last_reply_by":"zgl263885","last_touched":1686593776,"title":"求助！楼上的住户总是关我家水表阀门","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/947926","created":1686540277,"deleted":0,"content":"我是 2 楼，2 楼水表箱在 2 楼和 3 楼楼梯之间，时不时的有楼上人关水闸，持续一个月了。\r\n\r\n-------------------\r\n方案一：找物业，物业不管，说没有证据。\r\n\r\n方案二：买过一个带电池的摄像头（萤石 BC2 ），但持续录像只有三四个小时，就没电了。\r\n不能用省电模式，因为红外孔被挡住，一直是黑白画面，有人出现也不识别。\r\n\r\n方案三：找自来水公司关上水箱。不行，因为不方便抄水表，万一水管爆了也不方便及时关水。\r\n\r\n方案四：确定是楼上哪家住户，互相关水阀。\r\n\r\n肯定有人问为啥要关我水阀，说实话我也不知道，听我妈说是楼道门的原因，我妈喜欢把门开着，用石头抵住。这个楼上的人喜欢关着。","content_rendered":"<p>我是 2 楼，2 楼水表箱在 2 楼和 3 楼楼梯之间，时不时的有楼上人关水闸，持续一个月了。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>方案一：找物业，物业不管，说没有证据。</p>\n<p>方案二：买过一个带电池的摄像头（萤石 BC2 ），但持续录像只有三四个小时，就没电了。\n不能用省电模式，因为红外孔被挡住，一直是黑白画面，有人出现也不识别。</p>\n<p>方案三：找自来水公司关上水箱。不行，因为不方便抄水表，万一水管爆了也不方便及时关水。</p>\n<p>方案四：确定是楼上哪家住户，互相关水阀。</p>\n<p>肯定有人问为啥要关我水阀，说实话我也不知道，听我妈说是楼道门的原因，我妈喜欢把门开着，用石头抵住。这个楼上的人喜欢关着。</p>\n","last_modified":1686540277,"replies":71,"id":947926},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":56538,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8420,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":433522,"username":"zhwguest","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhwguest","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b633/f688/433522_mini.png?m=1685067457","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b633/f688/433522_normal.png?m=1685067457","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b633/f688/433522_large.png?m=1685067457","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b633/f688/433522_xlarge.png?m=1685067457","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b633/f688/433522_xlarge.png?m=1685067457","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b633/f688/433522_xlarge.png?m=1685067457","created":1564718222,"last_modified":1685067457},"last_reply_by":"strp","last_touched":1686598618,"title":"惊闻福州开始实行上网域名白名单","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/948137","created":1686577434,"deleted":0,"content":"[福州是否开始使用网络域名白名单？]( https://www.zhihu.com/question/602813176)\r\n\r\n各位，爽吧","content_rendered":"<p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/602813176\" rel=\"nofollow\">福州是否开始使用网络域名白名单？</a></p>\n<p>各位，爽吧</p>\n","last_modified":168